    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Layer of coarsely woven, heavyweight textile used in upholstery, fixed over webbing to form a seat cavity and to keep the stuffing from falling through.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
